data.description: This Beautiful Victorian Home is in town on a peaceful hill and neighborhood on the corner of S Victoria and Elizebeth St in Commerce GA. This home features large bedrooms and a large open kitchen with a breakfast island area that flows into the living room. This Classic Home has beautiful hardwood floors and open windows with plenty of sunlight. The front porch and swing are a wonderful touch with views of dogwood and oak trees. The City Library is just a few steps down the street and top-rated schools are nearby. This home is 10 minutes from I-85. 30 minutes to Athens, Braselton, and Buford. 35-40 minutes to Gainesville.
